comments: Okogie (MIN) legally contests Brown's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Thompson (BOS) legally contests Russell's (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Tatums (BOS) has his hands placed away from his body and briefly engages then disengages with McDaniels (MIN) during the screen.
Okogie (MIN) makes marginal contact with Tatum (BOS) in the post as Tatum receives the pass.
Tatum (BOS) initiates marginal contact with Okogie (MIN) on the dribble.
Okogie (MIN) legally contest Tatum's (BOS) shot attempt.
Thompson (BOS) and Towns (MIN) engage and disengage with each other during the rebound.
Tatum's (BOS) shot attempt does not make contact with the rim and BOS fails to release a second shot attempt prior to the shot clock expiring.
Smart (BOS) makes marginal contact with Russell's (MIN) arm as they engage prior to Russell receiving the pass.
Williams (BOS) momentarily places a hand to Russell's (MIN) front during the drive.
Williams (BOS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in McDaniels' (MIN) path.
Walker (BOS) naturally loses his footing as he dribbles.
Edwards (MIN) legally contests Tatum's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Brown (BOS) legally contests Russell's (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Williams (BOS) legally contests Russell's (MIN) jump shot attempt.
McDaniels (MIN) legally contests Tatum's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Edwards (MIN) legally contests Walker's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Brown (BOS) makes contact Russell's (MIN) body prior to Russell receiving the pass that affects his FOM and it should be whistled as a non-shooting foul.
Towns (MIN) moves into Tatum (BOS) and makes lower body contact that affects his jump shot attempt.
Russell (MIN) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Brown's (BOS) path.
Thompson (BOS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in McDaniels' (MIN) path and does not deliver any contact.
Towns (MIN) makes marginal contact with Thompson's (BOS) body on the dribble.
Tatum (BOS) makes marginal contact with McDaniels' (MIN) front during the play at the basket.
Hernangomez (MIN) commits a take foul on Smart (BOS).
Walker (BOS) makes marginal contact with Russell (MIN) during the drive.
Russell (MIN) makes marginal contact with Tatum's (BOS) arm as Tatum ends his dribble.
Thompson (BOS) wraps McDaniels (MIN) and holds him, affecting his ability to defend the shot attempt.
McDaniels (MIN) makes contact with Brown's (BOS) body during his driving shot attempt.
Smart (BOS) makes marginal contact with Russell's (MIN) off-arm during the drive.
Brown (BOS) makes clean contact with the ball.
Towns' (MIN) hand brushes across Smart's (BOS) arm in an attempt to commit a take foul but the contact is marginal.
Hernangomez (MIN) commits a take foul on Brown (BOS).
Towns (MIN) slightly kicks his leg out on the jump shot and makes marginal contact with Smart (BOS).
